<h1>Account Approved — Start Riding! 🎉</h1>
<p>Hi <strong style="color:#F0F0F0;">{{fullName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>
  Congratulations! Your NduthiRide rider account has been <strong style="color:#22C55E;">verified</strong>.
  You can now go online and start accepting rides and parcel deliveries.
</p>

<hr class="divider" />

<h2>Your Account</h2>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">Status</span>
  <span class="info-value"><span class="badge badge-success">Verified</span></span>
</div>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">License</span>
  <span class="info-value">{{licenseNumber}}</span>
</div>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">Bike</span>
  <span class="info-value">{{bikeModel}} · {{bikeRegistration}}</span>
</div>

<hr class="divider" />

<h2>Getting started</h2>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">1. Go Online</span>
  <span class="info-value">Toggle availability in the app</span>
</div>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">2. Accept Requests</span>
  <span class="info-value">Ride and parcel requests appear instantly</span>
</div>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">3. Get Paid</span>
  <span class="info-value">Earnings tracked in your dashboard</span>
</div>

<p style="text-align:center; margin-top: 32px;">
  <a href="{{appUrl}}" class="btn">Open Rider App</a>
</p>
